						               													<description>This is a pizza card game where the players play cards into a pizza pan while attempting to match adjacent slices with similar ingredients.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player is dealt four cards and one &amp;quot;ugh&amp;quot; card. On their turns, players play cards into the pizza pie pan. Whenever the ingredients from three adjacent slices match, the player score a point in each category of ingredient shown on those three cards and for all cards stacked beneath those cards. There is also one ingredient -- indicated by the &amp;quot;ugh&amp;quot; card -- that each player is trying to avoid.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Because some slices have more than one ingredient, players may end up scoring in favored categories and &amp;quot;ugh&amp;quot; categories at the same time. A player wins if he is the first to score 8 slices for each of his favored ingredients. He loses if he scores 8 slices of the &amp;quot;ugh&amp;quot; ingredient.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
